history.content:
Are you excited to make new friends? Friends who love game nights, trivia, TikTok, and more? Then, DataGood is the right place for you!
Interested in gaining a hands-on approach to projects dedicated to applying data science to the social good sector? Through DataGood @ Berkeley’s internal and external projects, members will have the opportunity to leverage their skills in a collaborative environment! Students of all backgrounds are welcome to apply. If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to us at any of the following links and join our Discord server for updates!
Website: datagood.berkeley.edu
Facebook: facebook.com/datagoodberkeley
Recruitment Discord: datagood.berkeley.edu/discord
Infosession Link: datagood.berkeley.edu/zoom
